Celebrate these courageous women of history and explore the Women Who Move Mountains collection on Paramount+: https://www.paramountplus.com/collections/women/

Emmeline Pankhurst: played by Tatiana Maslany and narrated by Kirby Howell-Baptiste.
Edith Garrud: played by Maria Blasucci and narrated by Kirby Howell-Baptiste.
Ida Tarbell: played by Shannon Woodward and narrated by Jon Gabrus.
